"1 cup unsalted butter, at room temperature","1 1/3 cups sugar","3 cups flour, plus more for rolling","1/2 teaspoon baking powder","1/2 teaspoon salt","1  egg plus 2 egg yolks","2 teaspoons vanilla extract","1/2 teaspoon peppermint extract, divided","20  to 25 drops red food coloring","15  to 20 drops green food coloring","10 ounce white chocolate, finely chopped","5 ounces peppermint candy canes or peppermint candies, finely crushed"